race.comment: FORTY TIMES (3) boasts a win over this mile journey and has been racing very consistently of late. Thornton stays in the saddle following that last-start runner-up finish and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. PERRI LASS (5) hit the frame over this track and trip at the latest effort and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim. Well placed to make a big impression. SAVVY BEE (8) has been thereabouts in recent efforts and gets the services of Rodd in the irons. Deserves serious consideration. OBSTRUCTIONIST (2) is a stayer resuming who should be hitting the line with gusto. WHATJEUDOIN' (7) next in line from the inside marble.
